着如何制作一款不做作的季节性游戏，”Thomas 说。 “你如何制作一个内容更新和游戏玩法变化感觉与世界交织在一起的故事？”</p><p> Towerborne 是 Xbox 发布的游戏，将于 2024 年通过 Steam 登陆 Xbox Series X / S、Xbox Game Pass 和 PC。 </p><div id="03e9a77c2729434db21b0d686d8a5f50"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4RhVFeNIBi0" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/sgf-2023"><em>在这里</em></a><em>了解夏季游戏节的所有新闻</em><em>！</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/towerborne-is-an-action-rpg-brawler-from-the-makers-of-the-banner-saga-185826861.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/towerborne-is-an-action-rpg-brawler-from-the-makers-of-the-banner-saga-185826861.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b56d1e88-fbfb-4f0d-9dd4-5adf5990b962</guid><dc:creator>威尔尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sun, 11 Jun 2023 18:58:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686510025</ingested><modified> 2023-06-11T19:00:34+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Lifestyle]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/72593f10-0888-11ee-bb9f-ea1cd11bbdd5" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:con